<p>The Little Mermaid is a fairy tale by Hans Christian Andersen.  It was written in 1837 in Denmark and has since been adapted to the screen across the world.  This site endeavors to keep track of the many adaptations regardless of obscurity.  </p>

<p>Click <a href="http://hca.gilead.org.il/li_merma.html">here</a> to be redirected to the complete text of The Little Mermaid the original fairy tale (translated to English).</p>

<p>In this site, any user may see the site's adaptations list, but in order to make a suggestion to add to the list or view all suggestions up for the administrator's consideration, one must be a registered user.</p>

